<plot>Adam Cagley stars as loveable Carter Bigelow, a 12-year-old outcast with one simple wish. But after a catastrophic mistake made by a slightly absentminded Genie, Carter finds himself among the often hysterical, always amazing chaos of a world where everyone's wishes are coming true at random...everyone's except his...a serendipitous disaster that can only be reversed by the boy himself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?095463</url></doc>
